---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

const title = '服务条款 - Momo工具箱';
const description = 'Momo工具箱服务条款：使用条款、免责声明与责任限制。';
const updatedZh = '2026年6月28日';
const updatedEn = 'June 28, 2026';
---

<BaseLayout title={title} description={description} canonical="https://www.web-tools.top/terms">
  <article class="legal-page">
    <div data-lang="zh">
      <h1>服务条款</h1>
      <p class="updated">最后更新：{updatedZh}</p>

      <p>欢迎使用 Momo工具箱（以下简称"本服务"）。使用本服务即表示您同意以下条款。如果您不同意任何条款，请停止使用本服务。</p>

      <h2>服务说明</h2>
      <p>本服务提供一系列在线工具，包括 JSON 格式化、Markdown 编辑器、二维码生成、密码生成器、Base64 编解码、URL 编解码、时间戳转换、哈希生成器、JWT 解码器、图片压缩、UUID 生成器、颜色格式转换、单位换算器等。所有工具均在浏览器本地运行，无需注册。</p>

      <h2>免费使用与未来可能的变化</h2>
      <p>本服务目前<strong>完全免费</strong>提供给您使用，无需注册。我们承诺<strong>基础工具功能将永久免费</strong>。</p>
      <p>未来我们可能：</p>
      <ul>
        <li>接入广告服务（如 Google AdSense）以支持网站运营，广告将仅在非工具操作区域展示</li>
        <li>推出部分高级功能或增值服务（如批量处理、API 调用、历史记录等），这些功能可能收费</li>
        <li>引入可选的账户系统，用于跨设备同步偏好设置</li>
      </ul>
      <p>任何重大变更我们都将在本页面提前告知。基础工具的核心功能不会因为上述变化而收费。</p>

      <h2>使用规则</h2>
      <p>使用本服务时，您同意：</p>
      <ul>
        <li>不将本服务用于任何违法或侵权的用途</li>
        <li>不试图破坏、干扰本网站的正常运行</li>
        <li>不通过自动化脚本对本服务进行恶意请求或攻击（合理范围内的 API 调用除外，如未来提供）</li>
        <li>自行对使用本工具处理的数据承担合规责任</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>免责声明</h2>
      <p>本服务按"现状"提供，不提供任何明示或暗示的保证，包括但不限于：</p>
      <ul>
        <li>对特定用途的适用性的保证</li>
        <li>对工具结果准确性、可靠性的保证</li>
        <li>对服务不间断、无错误的保证</li>
      </ul>
      <p>工具生成的结果（如密码、二维码、哈希值等）仅供便利使用，您应自行验证其正确性。对于因使用本服务产生的任何直接或间接损失，我们不承担责任。</p>

      <h2>责任限制</h2>
      <p>在任何情况下，我们均不对因使用或无法使用本服务而导致的任何损害（包括数据丢失、利润损失、业务中断等）承担责任。</p>

      <h2>知识产权</h2>
      <p>本网站的设计、排版、文案版权归我们所有。工具处理产生的内容归您所有。</p>

      <h2>第三方链接</h2>
      <p>本服务可能包含指向第三方网站（如 Cloudflare、Google）的链接。我们不对这些第三方网站的内容或隐私实践负责。</p>

      <h2>服务变更与终止</h2>
      <p>我们保留随时修改、暂停或终止本服务的权利，且无需事先通知。您可随时停止使用本服务。</p>

      <h2>条款变更</h2>
      <p>我们可能会不时更新本服务条款。更新后将在本页面发布并修改"最后更新"日期。继续使用本服务即表示您接受更新后的条款。</p>

      <h2>适用法律</h2>
      <p>本条款的解释与执行适用相关法律法规。如有争议，我们将本着友好协商的原则解决。</p>

      <h2>联系我们</h2>
      <p>如对本服务条款有任何疑问，请通过邮箱联系我们：<a href="mailto:1902243211@qq.com">1902243211@qq.com</a>。</p>
    </div>

    <div data-lang="en">
      <h1>Terms of Service</h1>
      <p class="updated">Last updated: {updatedEn}</p>

      <p>Welcome to Momo Toolbox ("the Service"). By using the Service, you agree to the following terms. If you do not agree with any of these terms, please stop using the Service.</p>

      <h2>Service Description</h2>
      <p>The Service provides a collection of online tools, including JSON formatter, Markdown editor, QR code generator, password generator, Base64 encoder/decoder, URL encoder/decoder, timestamp converter, hash generator, JWT decoder, image compressor, UUID generator, color converter, unit converter, and more. All tools run locally in your browser and require no registration.</p>

      <h2>Free Use and Possible Future Changes</h2>
      <p>The Service is currently <strong>completely free</strong> to use and requires no registration. We commit that <strong>core tool functionality will remain free forever</strong>.</p>
      <p>In the future we may:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Integrate advertising services (such as Google AdSense) to support operations. Ads will only be shown outside tool operation areas</li>
        <li>Introduce premium features or value-added services (such as batch processing, API access, history records) that may be charged</li>
        <li>Introduce an optional account system to sync preferences across devices</li>
      </ul>
      <p>Any significant changes will be announced on this page in advance. Core tool functionality will not be charged due to these changes.</p>

      <h2>Usage Rules</h2>
      <p>When using the Service, you agree to:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Not use the Service for any illegal or infringing purposes</li>
        <li>Not attempt to disrupt or interfere with the normal operation of the website</li>
        <li>Not make malicious requests or attacks via automated scripts (reasonable API usage excluded, if provided in the future)</li>
        <li>Take responsibility for the compliance of data you process with the tools</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Disclaimer</h2>
      <p>The Service is provided "as is" without any warranties, express or implied, including but not limited to:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Warranties of fitness for a particular purpose</li>
        <li>Warranties of accuracy or reliability of tool results</li>
        <li>Warranties of uninterrupted or error-free service</li>
      </ul>
      <p>Results generated by the tools (such as passwords, QR codes, hash values, etc.) are provided for convenience only. You should verify their correctness yourself. We are not liable for any direct or indirect losses arising from the use of the Service.</p>

      <h2>Limitation of Liability</h2>
      <p>In no event shall we be liable for any damages (including data loss, profit loss, business interruption, etc.) arising from the use of or inability to use the Service.</p>

      <h2>Intellectual Property</h2>
      <p>The design, layout, and copy of this website are owned by us. Content produced by the tools belongs to you.</p>

      <h2>Third-Party Links</h2>
      <p>The Service may contain links to third-party websites (such as Cloudflare, Google). We are not responsible for the content or privacy practices of these third-party sites.</p>

      <h2>Service Changes and Termination</h2>
      <p>We reserve the right to modify, suspend, or terminate the Service at any time without prior notice. You may stop using the Service at any time.</p>

      <h2>Changes to Terms</h2>
      <p>We may update these Terms of Service from time to time. Updates will be published on this page with an updated "Last updated" date. Continued use of the Service constitutes acceptance of the updated terms.</p>

      <h2>Governing Law</h2>
      <p>The interpretation and enforcement of these terms are governed by applicable laws. We will resolve disputes in a spirit of amicable negotiation.</p>

      <h2>Contact Us</h2>
      <p>For any questions about these Terms of Service, please contact us via email: <a href="mailto:1902243211@qq.com">1902243211@qq.com</a>.</p>
    </div>

    <div style="margin-top: 3rem; padding-top: 2rem; border-top: 1px solid var(--border);">
      <a href="/" style="color: var(--accent); text-decoration: underline;" data-zh="← 返回首页" data-en="← Back to Home">← 返回首页</a>
    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>